<lb n="1"/>Ōṁ namō nārāyaṇā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ya <g type="ddanda">.</g> surāsuraśirōratna
<lb n="3" break="no"/>marīcikhacitāṁhrayē vi
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ghnāṁdhakārasūryyāya gaṇā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>dhipatayē namaḥ <g type="ddanda">.</g> svasti sama
<lb n="6" break="no"/>stabhuvanāśraya śrīpṛthvīvallabha
<lb n="7"/>mahārājādhirāja paramēśvara pa
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ramabhaṭṭāraka satyāśrayakuḷatiḷaka cā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ḷukyābharaṇaṁ śrīmatpratāpacakra
<lb n="10" break="no"/>vartti jagadēkamalladēvara vijaya
<lb n="11" break="no"/>rājyamuttarōttarābhivṛddhipravarddhamā
<lb n="12" break="no"/>namācaṁdrārkkatāraṁbaraṁ salutta
<lb n="13"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> <unclear>rāja</unclear>dhāni kalyāṇapurada nelevīḍi
